commit.message:
Upgrade to actions/checkout version 3 and setup dependabot.

I certainly won't regret this commit.
Use the actual code supplied in the PR.
Adding a RETURN_THROWS macro. Thanks to negram for the lines.
Use RETURN_THROWS() to highlight that we have raised an exception
Fixed a couple of signatures to comply with latest changes
"ISO C90 forbids mixed declarations and code"

Fixed missing ifdef around function.

Apparently the stub generator is now producing different output so the change is huge.
Add missing test file to package.xml
Split package validation out to its own check, that should only run on master.
Allow ImagickDraw::setStrokeDashArray to take null as the parameter, to reset the dash array.
The docker default settings for output are annoying. We need to be able to see errors in the build more easily.
Restore main tests now package test is working.
